&lt;li&gt;String: a finite sequence of characters&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Regular Experssion Notations:&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;/image-1.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
